      <abstract id="aspace_00b844a770adc8db5522e3c2fa4ccaf6">This collection contains files covering the creation and activities of the William L. Reece Emeritus Center.</abstract>
      <physloc id="aspace_fa49e5c5ac3bfb1b3ebb2f766cab8ddb">The materials are located onsite in the department.</physloc>
